+// DOS-PORT (patch 0090, Phase 9 wave 20 W20B): finer-grain engine_tick
+// brackets opt-in. Originally drafted alongside flip-body brackets; the
+// flip-body brackets were parked to tests/probes/wip-w20b-flip-body-
+// brackets.diff (gitignored) per W20C probe results that showed sub-ms
+// for all 4 flip-body candidates. The engine_tick decomposition stays
